### Todo App CRUD Operations via Natural Language Chat
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1/simple-chat

### ================================
### CREATE TODOS - Various Examples
### ================================

### Create a work-related todo
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/simple-chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "I need to finish the quarterly report by Friday"
}

### Create a shopping todo
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/simple-chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Add buy groceries for dinner to my shopping list"
}

### Create a health-related todo
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/simple-chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Schedule dentist appointment next week"
}

### Create a personal todo
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/simple-chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Call mom to wish her happy birthday"
}

### Create a study-related todo
