### ================================
### UPDATE TODOS - Mark as Complete
### ================================

### Mark a specific todo as completed
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/simple-chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Mark the quarterly report task as completed"
}

### Mark shopping task as done
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/simple-chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "I finished buying groceries, mark it as done"
}

### Update todo details
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/simple-chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Change my dentist appointment task to include the specific date: March 15th"
}

### Mark multiple tasks as complete
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/simple-chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "I completed the grocery shopping and called my mom, please update those tasks"
}

